      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This driver-focused example utilizes a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox, providing precise shift throws and mechanical connectivity. The chassis is well-sorted, featuring a limited-slip differential and reinforced rear subframe mounting points\u2014a critical preventative measure for this platform. With a linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline and a responsive rack-and-pinion steering setup, this vehicle offers an unadulterated analog performance profile. The car exhibits honest patina consistent with a well-maintained enthusiast vehicle, ready for the canyons or daily spirited driving.",
